     SHORT="Spell checker designed to eventually replace ispell"

cat << EOF
Aspell is a spell checker designed to eventually replace ispell. Its main
feature is that it does a much better job of coming up with possible suggestions
than ispell does. It also has support for checking (La)TeX and HTML files, and
run-time support for other non-English languages.
EOF
